task.summary: Remove Chinese and make code more readable
Added similarity calc between query graph nodes and graph nodes.
Added print of the results and fixed bug in ranking.
Normalize ranking to be between 0 to 1
Changed the printout of the path results
Fixed another bug in rank calculation
Added treatment to return k vertices in the graph that are most similar to the first vertex in the query

Added 2 new functionality to the graph class: 1.function that finds all the leaves 2.function that finds all paths between given source and dest. 3.function that finds all paths between query source and all its leaves.
Implemented third step of multi path and fixing tests according to recent changes.
